Author: fishonthesun
Text: God, I could have written this if I knew how to put it into words so well. I'm sorry you're struggling this way too. We're here for you

Author: bruno_guy
Text: i dont know what to say but same, i feel you. some days i just want to fucking not exist or i tell myself let me just go eat whatever i want then i want to die. i hate how i only let myself eat the same foods every single day. its so annoying i dont allow myself to eat any other foods then like 10; i hate it so much.  i wish i can just eat something else and not think its bad for me or have to over exercise because its not a "safe" food.
